This is a summary view of OpenAddresses data. 188,115,574 addresses have been processed as of Sunday, Aug 30, 2015. Out of 1,111 total sources, 927 have completed. 111 sources failed cache, 73 cached but not processed. See the latest results with status maps.

We update these zipped global and regional address collections regularly:

  • Global collection
  • U.S. addresses (list of states by region):
    • U.S. Northeast collection
    • U.S. Midwest collection
    • U.S. South collection
    • U.S. West collection
  • Europe collection (list of European countries)
  • Asia/Oceania collection (list of Asian, Oceania countries)

The latest summary can always be found at data.openaddresses.io.
A plain text version of data on this page can be found at state.txt.
